    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >全新的地下世界</h2>在《死者国度》dlc中，玩家可以经由地铁口在地上和地下两个世界中探索和冒险。地下有着规模更大的地图，死者国度比没落平原的世界更加广阔，也有着数量更多的城镇。<br>还增加了两种全新的地形：火山区和冻原区。火山和冻原地形将影响车辆的引擎温度以及区域的物产情况，这两种新地形也会出现在《死者国度》地图的地下层中。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336570/extras/2dabcae6bf14db03bb3e4cc05a635bde.poster.avif?t=1722988053\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336570/extras/2dabcae6bf14db03bb3e4cc05a635bde.webm?t=1722988053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336570/extras/2dabcae6bf14db03bb3e4cc05a635bde.mp4?t=1722988053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >修路玩法</h2>地图上将会有史前建筑“道路局”，玩家可以在道路局花费资源和政治点要求道路局的机器人为自己修建道路。道路可以通过绝大多数的地形，但是不同地形所需要的资源是不同的（隧道，桥的开销将非常大）。玩家的车辆会在道路上行驶的更快。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336570/extras/3d825c2d299a112b5ca243fd0fc12fca.poster.avif?t=1722988053\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336570/extras/3d825c2d299a112b5ca243fd0fc12fca.webm?t=1722988053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336570/extras/3d825c2d299a112b5ca243fd0fc12fca.mp4?t=1722988053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >遗迹探险</h2>在地下大地图的各处，分布着包藏风险与收益的“遗迹”地点。玩家可以让队员离开车辆，在这些遗迹中探险，击败敌人，获得奖励（各种装备、修路点数及其他掉落物）。<br>地下世界中的这些废墟值得你冒险深入。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336570/extras/c06b5fd4c0f21cce3aa4558d2d33e565.poster.avif?t=1722988053\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336570/extras/c06b5fd4c0f21cce3aa4558d2d33e565.webm?t=1722988053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336570/extras/c06b5fd4c0f21cce3aa4558d2d33e565.mp4?t=1722988053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >新剧情</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336570/extras/40de563b3fb7521aebe36875095d739a.avif?t=1722988053\" width=620 height=268 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336570/extras/617b4d48509559d80f6fd701e9ca8b0e.avif?t=1722988053\" width=620 height=268 /></span>",
